embed.alt: A high-energy 15-second cinematic action trailer for “DIM SUM MASTER”, set in neon-lit Hong Kong night markets and steamy traditional teahouse kitchens, where legendary dim sum chefs secretly double as elite martial artists. Camera work is kinetic and aggressive with handheld close-ups, whip-pans, dramatic low angles, and sudden slow-motion impacts that smash back into real-time, all cut to an intense action soundtrack of Chinese war drums and modern bass. All dialogue and voiceover are in Cantonese, teasing ancient rivalries, honor, and mastery forged in the kitchen and in combat. The trailer ends on a steamer lid slamming shut, cutting to black with the title DIM SUM MASTER / 點心宗師 and the tagline “Honor Is Served Hot.” / 「真正嘅功夫，要趁熱上。」, steam fading into darkness.
